Package org.neo4j.bolt.txtracking

Class DefaultReconciledTransactionTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.bolt.txtracking.DefaultReconciledTransactionTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReconciledTransactionTracker
    public class DefaultReconciledTransactionTracker
extends Object
implements ReconciledTransactionTracker
    A ReconciledTransactionTracker used for standalone and clustered databases that have a reconciler and allow updates of the system database. Updates can happen asynchronously and the task of this tracker is to keep track of all fully reconciled operations.

      • initializationLock

        private final ReadWriteLock initializationLock
        Lock protects getLastReconciledTransactionId() and offerReconciledTransactionId(long) from running concurrently with enable(long) and reading/updating a stale sequence. This is especially required when re-initialization happens at runtime and not during start of the lifecycle. Re-initialization can happen after a store copy of the system database.
